rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0001
rows.name:
Adel-sama, to think the Iiran seal
would fall into the Grail's hands...

rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0002
rows.name: He was even scarier than I thought.

rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0003
rows.name: I was no match for someone that evil.

rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0004
rows.name:
There's no way I could have stopped
him attacking the city...

rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0005
rows.name: But I'll still regret it to my dying day.

rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0006
rows.name:
Oh, I'm sorry. You must have come to
report to the king, and now I've held
you up with my chatter...

rows.label: tlk70000080_03_msg0007
rows.name: I won't hold you up any longer.
